                    "ability_type": "automatic",
                    "name": "Cold Healing",
                    "text": "Calathgars are healed by cold. Anytime a calathgar would take cold damage, it instead regains 1d6 Hit Points (regardless of the amount of damage the cold effect would have caused). In severe cold or colder environments, calathgars gain fast healing 1.",
